icons_text: The Toolbox Bodensee e.V. is a non-profit maker and hack space in Markdorf on Lake Constance, which tries to create a cozy atmosphere for members as well as guests in which people with similar interests can meet and exchange information. We have a large club house where everyone is welcome to relax in the lounge or in the ball pool, to participate in lectures or workshops, to work with the tools in the workshop or to exchange ideas with the other people here.
