pre_about_header: The Creative Workshop – Toolbox Bodensee e.V.
---
pre_about_text:

The Toolbox Bodensee e.V. is a non-profit association, which offers a space to IT-interested and other tinkerers for creative thinking and acting. With the help of professional equipment common projects can be realized here.

In our creative workshop with wood workshop, screen printing and electronics laboratory you have a lot of space for creativity. 
We are looking forward to your ideas for new projects and to your knowledge!
